{"tid":2171843,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"官場三傻 - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-08-24T08:37:21.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-24T08:37:21.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"d8dd8d0be4fbb896048c473ab073e33ff01a7b11","tid":2171843,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-24T08:37:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200824/GSO5Y4C3FJHHFBWLPA6OXHNHXU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200824%2FGSO5Y4C3FJHHFBWLPA6OXHNHXU%2F&d=aCvg504CNSeS5FxaNurzstUsrLV3ynd9sCeqRx8pZcg%3D&h=bf619c04\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200824%2FGSO5Y4C3FJHHFBWLPA6OXHNHXU%2F&h=9e9a18e2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200824/GSO5Y4C3FJHHFBWLPA6OXHNHXU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官場三傻 - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2Mj6FQw9u57NeDliolXMALqp9oM=/801x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/LP4WGVLI2FGHFDSB7WL3KWG7XI.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2Mj6FQw9u57NeDliolXMALqp9oM%3D%2F801x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FLP4WGVLI2FGHFDSB7WL3KWG7XI.png&h=f0ffe895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n張建宗鼓勵年輕人逆巿搵工，。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗似乎把年輕人失業率高這個問題，一下子推向年輕人揀擇，有工不肯做，對就業巿場有錯誤期待。請問他說這番話之前，有沒有經過巿場調查？是不是真的有很多食肆請不到人洗碗？而年輕人有碗不肯洗？<br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎肆虐，政府迄今不封關，令香港飲食業成為重災區。限制堂食人數及晚餐禁食令後，許多餐廳為求生存，轉做外賣，食肆可洗的碗寥寥可數，令洗碗工的崗位削減。張建宗希望年輕人去洗甚麼碗？洗即用即棄的發泡膠碗，洗乾淨了再循環使用？還是學中國餐廳，把食客吃剩的食物洗乾淨消毒，再賣給下一手？<br />\n<br />\n張建宗離地膠論與陳肇始的「禁堂食先知咁多人要返工」，以及羅致光的「打風先知咁多人戶外工作」不相伯仲，三傻鬥傻，難分勝負。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭治下，問責高官有共同特徵：全部不需要問責，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。我們會覺得香港是蠢人福地。"}]}